1
00:00:07,640 --> 00:00:11,070
Until then, Seon Hee thought

2
00:00:11,070 --> 00:00:14,860
she didn't have the right to love Jae Min.

3
00:00:16,760 --> 00:00:19,260
It's because...

4
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:26,450
she still regrets that day's moment.

5
00:00:27,700 --> 00:00:30,790
Lee Jae Min, do you want to come and hang out at my house?
[6 years ago]

6
00:00:30,790 --> 00:00:34,650
I can't. My brother will come soon, so I have to go home.

7
00:00:34,650 --> 00:00:37,220
- Do you have an older brother?
- Yes.

8
00:00:37,220 --> 00:00:39,650
My brother needs me.

9
00:00:39,650 --> 00:00:42,940
I'm going home now. See you tomorrow, Kang Seon Hee.

10
00:00:42,940 --> 00:00:45,750
I have a cat in my house.

11
00:00:47,210 --> 00:00:50,050
- A cat?
- Yes.

12
00:00:53,560 --> 00:00:57,060
Then shall I hang out at your place for a little bit?

13
00:01:04,960 --> 00:01:08,990
[So Mang]

14
00:01:08,990 --> 00:01:12,240
You've never wished that your brother didn't exist, have you?

15
00:01:12,240 --> 00:01:13,590
Why do you ask about that?

16
00:01:13,590 --> 00:01:16,230
Because I wish I didn't have my older brother.

17
00:01:16,230 --> 00:01:18,650
He always says something weird.

18
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:30,110
[Episode 15: Pieces of memory]

19
00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:41,440
So Mang, did you see this?

20
00:01:44,470 --> 00:01:46,050
Are the trainee teacher and the male high school student dating?

21
00:01:46,050 --> 00:01:47,330
Does anyone know who the boy is?

22
00:01:47,370 --> 00:01:50,270
Who's that boy? It's too bad that his face is hard to see.

23
00:01:50,270 --> 00:01:51,900
Hey, did you see this?

24
00:01:51,900 --> 00:01:53,240
Isn't she the trainee teacher from Class 5 of the second year?

25
00:01:53,240 --> 00:01:55,350
- Is that Ms. So Mang?
- Their identity will get exposed soon.

26
00:01:55,350 --> 00:01:57,450
You never know, so I'm not going to take any sides.

27
00:01:57,450 --> 00:02:00,040
- Both of their school life is over now.
- What did they do at that hour?

28
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:02,910
It's insane. I didn't think that teacher would be someone like that.

29
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:09,600
I definitely told you on the first day of your work.

30
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:12,450
That you shouldn't see students outside of school.

31
00:02:12,450 --> 00:02:14,730
I'm sorry, sir.

32
00:02:16,580 --> 00:02:18,780
A disciplinary committee will open soon.

33
00:02:18,780 --> 00:02:22,630
In the worst-case scenario, you might have to quit.

34
00:02:24,610 --> 00:02:26,970
This boy is Lee Jae Min, right?

35
00:02:28,200 --> 00:02:34,700
The reason is obvious for you two to meet, so if you explain the situation well, you might not get disciplinary action.

36
00:02:36,610 --> 00:02:38,450
Sir.

37
00:02:41,850 --> 00:02:46,410
I don't want Jae Min to be involved in this.

38
00:02:46,410 --> 00:02:49,770
Han So Mang! Do you think this is not a big deal?

39
00:02:49,770 --> 00:02:53,600
If you quit with this kind of scandal, you'll never be able to become a teacher!

40
00:02:54,850 --> 00:02:59,320
I'll give you time until tomorrow, so think about how you'll explain this.

41
00:03:15,380 --> 00:03:17,740
Is Ms. So Mang inside?

42
00:03:20,570 --> 00:03:21,980
[Broadcasting Room]

43
00:03:21,980 --> 00:03:23,950
Ms. So Mang.

44
00:03:31,990 --> 00:03:35,620
Staying out of this is a help to her right now.

45
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:43,930
I heard that person in the photo is Ms. So Mang.

46
00:03:45,130 --> 00:03:48,770
Since Kwon Ho Jun knows about it, I bet the entire school knows it now.

47
00:03:48,770 --> 00:03:51,310
But seriously, the comments are horrifying.

48
00:03:51,310 --> 00:03:53,540
Ms. So Mang is not that kind of person to do so!

49
00:03:53,540 --> 00:03:56,420
Right, Ms. So Mang is not someone to do so.

50
00:03:56,420 --> 00:04:00,820
It's terrible for her, too, but people are going crazy to figure out who the boy is.

51
00:04:00,820 --> 00:04:08,270
But what kind of reason does a teacher have to meet up with a student at night?

52
00:04:14,620 --> 00:04:16,180
Gyu Ri, do you want to go to the restroom with me?

53
00:04:16,180 --> 00:04:18,050
Yes, sure.

54
00:04:20,210 --> 00:04:21,580
Stop it.

55
00:04:21,580 --> 00:04:23,430
But it's true.

56
00:04:24,150 --> 00:04:25,880
Jae Min.

57
00:04:27,260 --> 00:04:30,020
Can we talk for a second?

58
00:04:32,660 --> 00:04:37,080
Did you talk with Ms. So Mang?

59
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:41,070
She's been avoiding me since.

60
00:04:42,170 --> 00:04:45,600
Actually, it's something that'll resolve if I step up.

61
00:04:47,730 --> 00:04:49,700
Let's wait for now.

62
00:04:49,700 --> 00:04:53,880
She must have an idea as well.

63
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:57,650
I don't like that.

64
00:04:57,650 --> 00:05:00,590
It feels like I keep getting protected.

65
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:05,590
I'm sorry, but I'll get going first.

66
00:05:13,290 --> 00:05:15,210
Yoon Bo Mi!

67
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:19,870
I have something to tell you.

68
00:05:22,820 --> 00:05:25,220
Are romance comics that fun?

69
00:05:25,220 --> 00:05:27,440
I think you'll see textbooks less than that.

70
00:05:27,440 --> 00:05:33,560
It's because you don't know. It has the truth of life that you can't even learn in textbooks.

71
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,080
Why don't you take a look?

72
00:05:35,080 --> 00:05:38,320
Don't give him attention. He'll get overwhelmed on his own.

73
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:41,950
What I'm doing is way better than you playing games!

74
00:05:42,770 --> 00:05:47,090
So, how long are you going to hang around with us?

75
00:05:47,090 --> 00:05:49,960
Do you think you'll get an answer by avoiding it forever like this?

76
00:05:51,630 --> 00:05:53,950
Then what about you?

77
00:05:53,950 --> 00:05:57,500
Do you think she will recognize you if you watch her from afar?

78
00:05:57,500 --> 00:06:00,350
You said Yoon Bo Mi is the type of person who digs a hole by herself.

79
00:06:00,350 --> 00:06:04,410
I think you should make up with her before you two get more awkward.

80
00:06:04,410 --> 00:06:06,650
You better worry about yourself!

81
00:06:06,650 --> 00:06:10,450
You better apologize to Yoon Bo Mi for saying such harsh words.

82
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:16,200
Is that what you call a collective monologue?

83
00:06:16,200 --> 00:06:18,120
They are both saying what they want to say individually.

84
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:22,010
It's like the saying, "A Buddhist monk can't shave his own head."

85
00:06:22,010 --> 00:06:24,560
- I think that's correct.
- Right?

86
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:26,820
What do you want to tell me?

87
00:06:29,230 --> 00:06:31,540
I heard that you broke up with your boyfriend.

88
00:06:32,710 --> 00:06:35,360
I knew that would come soon.

89
00:06:35,360 --> 00:06:37,070
Why do you think that way?

90
00:06:37,070 --> 00:06:41,630
It's because he was not on your level! You should date someone more suitable for you.

91
00:06:41,630 --> 00:06:44,990
For example, someone like me?

92
00:06:44,990 --> 00:06:50,510
I'm sorry, but I think you are worse since you divide people into levels.

93
00:06:50,510 --> 00:06:52,970
Then I'll get going now.

94
00:06:52,970 --> 00:06:56,840
Hey! You dated such a loser, but you can't date me?

95
00:07:02,230 --> 00:07:05,050
What the heck was that?

96
00:07:05,050 --> 00:07:07,180
Hey, Choi Jin Young.

97
00:07:11,970 --> 00:07:13,470
What bastard did this?!

98
00:07:13,470 --> 00:07:16,720
It wasn't a lie that you like Yoon Bo Mi. Right?

99
00:07:20,300 --> 00:07:22,220
Seriously!

100
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:27,380
I thought it was my last chance.

101
00:07:28,700 --> 00:07:33,990
The last chance to tell you my true feeling.

102
00:08:04,410 --> 00:08:10,350
But you were moving away from me...

103
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:14,790
faster than I thought.

104
00:08:24,270 --> 00:08:26,840
Apologetic feelings...

105
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:31,400
Hopeless feelings...

106
00:08:33,500 --> 00:08:36,930
They keep getting tangled up.

107
00:08:41,780 --> 00:08:44,320
I hope Ms. So Mang is okay.

108
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:48,310
It's a misunderstanding, so wouldn't it get resolved soon?

109
00:08:48,310 --> 00:08:52,390
Lee Jae Min, do you know anything about it?

110
00:08:52,390 --> 00:08:54,230
Lee Jae Min!

111
00:08:54,230 --> 00:08:57,150
What? What did you say?

112
00:08:57,150 --> 00:09:01,340
You are close with Ms. So Mang. Did you hear anything from her?

113
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:08,870
Did you see the photo that came up on the anonymous community?

114
00:09:08,870 --> 00:09:11,390
Of course, I saw it.
[Meeting Room]

115
00:09:11,390 --> 00:09:13,620
It's that trainee teacher.
[Meeting Room]

116
00:09:13,620 --> 00:09:15,880
[Meeting Room]

117
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:27,500
Oh, that's right. I'll be back from the classroom.

118
00:09:27,500 --> 00:09:29,140
What?

119
00:09:35,990 --> 00:09:38,160
So Mang.

120
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:41,220
Are you sure you won't regret this?

121
00:09:42,560 --> 00:09:44,330
Sir.

122
00:09:45,180 --> 00:09:50,530
The time when I hid behind Ha Min,

123
00:09:50,530 --> 00:09:54,040
I regretted it for a long time.

124
00:09:55,640 --> 00:10:00,530
I don't want to do that anymore.

125
00:10:16,690 --> 00:10:21,210
I know that you have an emotional debt to Ha Min.

126
00:10:21,210 --> 00:10:29,120
I think this is the only thing that I can do for Ha Min.

127
00:10:38,280 --> 00:10:40,630
Excuse me, sir.

128
00:10:40,630 --> 00:10:42,880
Do you know where Ms. So Mang is?

129
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:46,740
Oh, Jae Min. Ms. So Mang is now...

130
00:10:46,740 --> 00:10:49,910
Ms. So Mang decided to quit her work as a trainee teacher.

131
00:10:51,460 --> 00:10:53,550
She made that decision on her own.

132
00:10:53,550 --> 00:10:58,130
If you don't want her decision to go to waste, you should stay out of this.

133
00:11:06,410 --> 00:11:08,260
Be quiet!

134
00:11:12,750 --> 00:11:18,010
Sir! Why is Ms. So Mang not joining the class today?

135
00:11:18,010 --> 00:11:20,700
Oh, you guys didn't hear about it.

136
00:11:20,700 --> 00:11:24,010
- She handed in her resignation letter.
- What?

137
00:11:24,010 --> 00:11:25,620
- Did Ms. So Mang quit?
- Did you hear about it?

138
00:11:25,620 --> 00:11:30,460
I mean, she did hand in her resignation letter, but she basically got fired.

139
00:11:30,460 --> 00:11:34,180
Who would leave a teacher who had an affair with a student in school?

140
00:11:34,180 --> 00:11:37,700
It's so embarrassing.

141
00:11:39,390 --> 00:11:43,400
Actually, she seemed like a not-so-good-one from the beginning.

142
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:48,400
How can a trainee try to correct an actual teacher in his class?

143
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:52,740
Those who don't even know hierarchy don't have the right to become a teacher!

144
00:11:52,740 --> 00:11:55,610
Ms. So Mang is not that kind of person!

145
00:12:00,740 --> 00:12:03,470
Hey, what do you know about it?

146
00:12:03,470 --> 00:12:09,450
Didn't you see her making a fuss when I was telling you a ghost story about the suicide student?

147
00:12:09,450 --> 00:12:12,160
It's just a lame story, but she pretended to be righteous alone.

148
00:12:12,160 --> 00:12:16,950
Is it a lame story when a student kills themselves?

149
00:12:16,950 --> 00:12:21,410
This punk... You come out here. How dare you talk back when a teacher is talking?

150
00:12:21,410 --> 00:12:23,880
The boy in that ghost story!

151
00:12:25,290 --> 00:12:28,770
He's my older brother, who committed suicide six years ago.

152
00:12:28,770 --> 00:12:31,770
- Did he have an older brother?
- What's all this?

153
00:12:31,770 --> 00:12:34,960
Wasn't he an only child?

154
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:38,790
And Ms. So Mang was my brother's only friend.

155
00:12:40,410 --> 00:12:46,410
She was the only person who told me about my brother.

156
00:12:46,410 --> 00:12:50,010
So please don't talk carelessly about them!

157
00:12:50,010 --> 00:12:53,140
Both Ms. So Mang...

158
00:12:53,140 --> 00:12:55,350
and my brother.

159
00:13:03,540 --> 00:13:05,470
Where are you going?

160
00:13:05,470 --> 00:13:07,400
Sit down!

161
00:13:51,830 --> 00:13:54,660
I knew you would be here.

162
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:09,910
- Did you guys know about it?
- That Jae Min had an older brother?

163
00:14:09,910 --> 00:14:11,720
Of course, I didn't know about it as well.

164
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:14,110
- You also didn't know? Did you make any mistakes?

165
00:14:14,110 --> 00:14:15,570
I don't know. I'm not sure.

166
00:14:15,570 --> 00:14:18,320
Did I make any mistakes to him?

167
00:14:29,540 --> 00:14:33,350
How can short kids like me jump over if the gate is this tall?

168
00:14:35,110 --> 00:14:36,860
Seon Hee.

169
00:14:39,410 --> 00:14:41,940
Here's an approval paper to leave the school early.

170
00:14:48,870 --> 00:14:51,380
You are always like this.

171
00:14:51,380 --> 00:14:54,660
When did I ask you to do this for me?

172
00:14:54,660 --> 00:14:59,060
Why do you keep doing things that I never asked for in the name of consideration and make me a fool?

173
00:14:59,060 --> 00:15:05,210
Do I look like a kid who can't do anything without your help?

174
00:15:07,500 --> 00:15:09,100
No.

175
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:15,660
I thought I was like a child who always got help from you.

176
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:23,300
I'm hesitant, but unlike me, you always showed it with your actions.

177
00:15:25,090 --> 00:15:27,760
I'm jealous of that part of you,

178
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:30,100
and I'm thankful to you.

179
00:15:31,670 --> 00:15:33,800
So if...

180
00:15:35,310 --> 00:15:40,410
I drift apart from you, I'll be very sad.

181
00:15:45,590 --> 00:15:48,730
Yoon Bo Mi, you are unnecessarily kind.

182
00:15:50,880 --> 00:15:53,230
So you make it hard even to hate you.

183
00:16:05,700 --> 00:16:08,420
Yoon Bom, did you...

184
00:16:08,420 --> 00:16:10,800
did you ask for extra potato noodles?

185
00:16:10,800 --> 00:16:14,340
Yes. And I also asked for extra cheese.

186
00:16:22,770 --> 00:16:25,820
Will Lee Jae Min be okay?

187
00:16:27,050 --> 00:16:28,840
He'll be all right.

188
00:16:28,840 --> 00:16:32,360
Jae Min is a stronger person than we think.

189
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:36,400
That's his problem! He always puts up on his own.

190
00:16:36,400 --> 00:16:40,470
Wouldn't it be better if he shared it with the people around him?

191
00:16:40,470 --> 00:16:43,240
It's frustrating.

192
00:16:43,240 --> 00:16:45,160
Seon Hee.

193
00:16:47,240 --> 00:16:53,750
I thought it was all for you when I tried to give up Jae Min for you.

194
00:16:53,750 --> 00:16:56,230
But I think I thought it wrong.

195
00:16:57,830 --> 00:17:03,380
I just didn't have the confidence to love Jae Min as much as you did.

196
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:09,540
But Jin Young was different.

197
00:17:10,630 --> 00:17:15,490
When I saw you and Jin Young together,

198
00:17:15,490 --> 00:17:17,670
I got very jealous.

199
00:17:18,580 --> 00:17:23,670
There's nothing to be jealous about him and me!

200
00:17:29,050 --> 00:17:34,650
So are you saying you really do have feelings for Choi Jin Young?

201
00:17:34,650 --> 00:17:39,550
Yes. I still have feelings for Jin Young.

202
00:17:40,780 --> 00:17:44,940
I don't know how he feels about me.

203
00:17:47,610 --> 00:17:50,070
Seriously, what are you guys doing?

204
00:17:50,070 --> 00:17:53,160
Did you two decide to make me die from frustration?

205
00:17:54,240 --> 00:17:56,060
Hey, Choi Jin Young.

206
00:17:56,990 --> 00:17:58,300
What bastard did this?!

207
00:17:58,300 --> 00:18:01,450
It wasn't a lie that you like Yoon Bo Mi. Right?

208
00:18:03,010 --> 00:18:04,750
You're right.

209
00:18:05,950 --> 00:18:08,240
When did I start...

210
00:18:09,440 --> 00:18:12,310
to like Yoon Bo Mi this much?

211
00:18:16,700 --> 00:18:19,130
It's frustrating.

212
00:18:19,130 --> 00:18:23,280
You are usually so good at saying things, but why can't you say you have feelings for Yoon Bom?

213
00:18:23,280 --> 00:18:25,290
It's because I don't have the right.

214
00:18:25,290 --> 00:18:28,460
Yoon Bo Mi is in trouble because of me.

215
00:18:31,050 --> 00:18:35,500
Yes! Tell that to her, not me.

216
00:18:35,500 --> 00:18:39,270
Yoon Bom is the one to decide if you have the right or not.

217
00:18:41,140 --> 00:18:45,750
If I look at things like that, you two look pretty good together.

218
00:18:47,700 --> 00:18:49,650
You can eat now.

219
00:18:49,650 --> 00:18:53,050
- Seon Hee, Iâ€”
- You can go.

220
00:18:53,050 --> 00:18:55,200
I'll take care of this.

221
00:19:11,320 --> 00:19:13,040
Hello?

222
00:19:17,310 --> 00:19:19,880
Jin Young, where are you?

223
00:19:19,880 --> 00:19:23,110
I have something to tell you.

224
00:19:27,630 --> 00:19:29,490
Hello?

225
00:20:01,370 --> 00:20:03,590
Why did you do that?

226
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:07,400
I had to say that at some point.

227
00:20:08,340 --> 00:20:13,380
Actually, I feel better after saying it since it takes a load off my chest.

228
00:20:14,600 --> 00:20:22,300
I knew that my brother could bear it, all thanks to you.

229
00:20:24,760 --> 00:20:26,580
But...

230
00:20:28,660 --> 00:20:32,090
I think I just wanted to look away from that fact.

231
00:20:33,890 --> 00:20:36,400
If I admit that,

232
00:20:37,920 --> 00:20:41,220
then I need to find another person to blame.

233
00:20:44,990 --> 00:20:46,810
Jae Min.

234
00:20:46,810 --> 00:20:48,970
I'm sorry, Ms. So Mang.

235
00:20:54,150 --> 00:20:56,070
That day...

236
00:20:57,550 --> 00:20:59,930
can you tell me...

237
00:21:02,200 --> 00:21:09,300
what happened to Ha Min?

238
00:21:16,700 --> 00:21:23,000
I remember it was raining on that day.

239
00:21:25,100 --> 00:21:30,820
I promised my brother to come home right after my tutoring.

240
00:21:31,550 --> 00:21:35,260
But my friend asked me to hang out at their place.

241
00:21:36,350 --> 00:21:39,550
You've never wished that your brother didn't exist, have you?

242
00:21:39,550 --> 00:21:40,690
Why do you ask about that?

243
00:21:40,690 --> 00:21:43,420
Because I wish I didn't have my older brother.

244
00:21:43,420 --> 00:21:45,640
He always says something weird.

245
00:21:54,680 --> 00:21:56,590
I also...

246
00:21:58,320 --> 00:22:01,240
I also wish my brother didn't exist sometimes.

247
00:22:08,510 --> 00:22:10,370
Jae Min.

248
00:22:13,600 --> 00:22:16,040
Jae Min, are you okay?

249
00:22:18,260 --> 00:22:19,960
Seon Hee!

250
00:22:20,880 --> 00:22:26,280
Do you remember the guy you saw on the day my brother died?

251
00:22:27,570 --> 00:22:29,130
What?

252
00:22:30,470 --> 00:22:35,000
Because of him, my mom and dad

253
00:22:35,000 --> 00:22:38,580
don't have any expectations of me.

